WEBVTT

01:42.840 --> 01:45.000
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL
HIDDEN LOVE BY ZHU YI

01:50.080 --> 01:51.200
Hello?

01:57.360 --> 01:58.280
Yes, that's me.

02:00.320 --> 02:01.240
All right.

02:01.960 --> 02:03.480
Okay, I see.

02:06.120 --> 02:07.400
- What is it?
- What's up?

02:09.800 --> 02:10.919
I passed my interview.

02:11.000 --> 02:12.200
- Really?
- Is that true?

02:13.000 --> 02:15.160
- Awesome! You have an internship already.
- What is it?

02:15.240 --> 02:16.760
- What is it?
- Here's the thing.

02:16.840 --> 02:17.880
It means

02:18.360 --> 02:19.720
that I can't go to the party.

02:19.800 --> 02:22.040
No way! You promised me!

02:22.120 --> 02:23.160
Hurry up and get ready.

02:42.200 --> 02:44.240
How was the interview with him?

02:44.880 --> 02:46.680
Well, it was like usual.

02:47.160 --> 02:48.240
How is that?

02:48.840 --> 02:50.480
There was nothing special.

02:51.920 --> 02:54.240
I guess I should give you some advice.

02:54.320 --> 02:55.320
First--

02:55.400 --> 02:56.960
Stop. Please don't.

02:57.520 --> 02:58.720
Your ways with Chen Qiang

02:58.800 --> 03:00.080
aren't suitable for Wangwang.

03:00.160 --> 03:01.800
Wangwang should

03:01.880 --> 03:02.720
depend on herself.

03:02.800 --> 03:03.840
Thank you.

03:04.880 --> 03:06.360
All right then. All the best!

03:06.440 --> 03:07.680
Good luck to me.

03:18.440 --> 03:21.000
Compared to the intended results,

03:21.600 --> 03:24.400
can we improve on the details?

03:25.440 --> 03:27.360
Jiaxu, what do you think?

03:30.880 --> 03:32.200
In my opinion,

03:32.680 --> 03:33.840
this is good to go

03:34.480 --> 03:36.720
since it reconstructs the design
of the previous scene

03:37.280 --> 03:39.400
and the functions are optimized.

03:39.480 --> 03:41.000
Regarding the lighting,

03:41.080 --> 03:42.400
can we refine it

03:42.480 --> 03:43.600
a little bit more?

03:43.680 --> 03:46.000
It looks rather stiff to me.

03:47.200 --> 03:48.760
Our game's weather system

03:48.840 --> 03:50.240
should update in real-time.

03:50.320 --> 03:53.880
At present, the daytime looks fine.

03:53.960 --> 03:55.520
However, I think

03:56.200 --> 03:57.760
we can still adjust the night view.

03:58.440 --> 03:59.600
Look at that…

04:04.960 --> 04:06.120
Siyun.

04:06.200 --> 04:07.880
- Are you okay, Siyun?
- What's wrong?

04:07.960 --> 04:08.840
What's wrong, Siyun?

04:09.840 --> 04:10.680
Have a seat.

04:10.760 --> 04:11.720
Are you okay?

04:11.800 --> 04:13.160
I'll get her a cup of water, Jiaxu.

04:13.240 --> 04:14.160
Okay, go.

04:17.040 --> 04:18.399
Do you need to go to the hospital?

04:18.959 --> 04:19.880
It's okay.

04:19.959 --> 04:21.480
It's a chronic gastric problem.

04:21.560 --> 04:23.480
Siyun, I think you should go
to the hospital

04:23.560 --> 04:26.200
- or it will get worse.
- It's okay. I'm used to it now.

04:26.280 --> 04:27.200
- Honey.
- Li Xun.

04:27.280 --> 04:28.400
- Li Xun.
- Are you okay?

04:28.480 --> 04:29.600
Is it gastric pain again?

04:29.680 --> 04:30.800
Let's go to the hospital.

04:30.880 --> 04:31.760
I'm not going.

04:31.840 --> 04:32.800
Listen to me. Come.

04:32.880 --> 04:34.880
This is a critical period. I must be here.

04:34.960 --> 04:37.320
- We're all here.
- Your health is more important.

04:37.400 --> 04:39.200
- Yes.
- They're all telling you to go.

04:39.280 --> 04:41.240
Is work more important than your health?

04:41.320 --> 04:43.320
- Yes, just go.
- You can come back to work later.

04:43.400 --> 04:44.400
- Go on.
- Help her up.

04:44.480 --> 04:46.040
- Let's go.
- Go, Siyun. I mean it.

04:46.120 --> 04:47.320
I'll leave this to you, Jiaxu.

04:47.400 --> 04:48.760
Stay here. I'll take her.

04:48.840 --> 04:51.040
- Li Xun, I'll get the car.
- Okay.

04:51.120 --> 04:53.160
- Be careful, Li Xun.
- Be careful.

04:53.240 --> 04:55.160
Goodness, Ning Wei.

04:55.240 --> 04:56.480
You're packing so many things.

04:56.560 --> 04:57.920
Are you going to a beauty pageant?

04:58.880 --> 05:00.920
It's my first trip with Chen Qiang.

05:01.000 --> 05:03.080
More cosmetics and clothes are necessary.

05:03.800 --> 05:04.840
Look at you.

05:04.920 --> 05:06.160
It's so nice to be single.

05:06.240 --> 05:07.840
You don't have to bring anything.

05:07.920 --> 05:10.360
I'm going for an internship,

05:10.440 --> 05:11.520
not a beauty pageant.

05:12.040 --> 05:12.880
That's true.

05:13.800 --> 05:16.320
Sangsang, you look like
a working professional today.

05:16.400 --> 05:17.440
Nonsense.

05:18.120 --> 05:19.320
Yes, you do.

05:19.400 --> 05:20.280
Good job.

05:20.920 --> 05:23.120
I wanted to dress more formally,

05:23.200 --> 05:25.240
so my boss won't think that I'm weird.

05:25.880 --> 05:26.880
By the way,

05:26.960 --> 05:28.560
you'll be staying in the dorm alone.

05:28.640 --> 05:29.600
Will you be scared?

05:31.160 --> 05:32.280
I'll be okay.

05:32.360 --> 05:33.640
Don't worry. Don't be scared.

05:33.720 --> 05:35.640
I'm interning only two hours away

05:35.720 --> 05:36.920
from the dorm.

05:37.000 --> 05:38.960
If you feel scared, call me.
I'll come right away.

05:39.960 --> 05:42.200
Who needs you to accompany her?

05:42.280 --> 05:43.960
She has a boyfriend.

05:44.040 --> 05:45.080
Let me interview you.

05:45.160 --> 05:46.720
Are you getting an internship so early

05:46.800 --> 05:48.760
so you can stay
to spend more time with him?

05:50.400 --> 05:51.640
It's honestly to intern--

05:51.720 --> 05:53.040
Okay, say no more.

05:53.120 --> 05:54.600
We understand.

05:54.680 --> 05:56.240
Your perfume smells so strong.

05:56.320 --> 05:57.160
Does it smell nice?

05:59.480 --> 06:00.680
It's a bit too much.

06:00.760 --> 06:01.600
Is that so?

06:02.680 --> 06:03.600
I think it's all right.

06:07.560 --> 06:08.760
What is it?

06:08.840 --> 06:10.120
Hello, little demon.

06:11.400 --> 06:12.400
I've been busy dating.

06:13.280 --> 06:14.360
By the way,

06:14.440 --> 06:15.560
have you booked your flight?

06:15.640 --> 06:16.760
I'll pick you up.

06:22.240 --> 06:24.960
Didn't I tell you that I'll be interning
and not coming back?

06:25.040 --> 06:26.800
Didn't Dad and Mom tell you?

06:26.880 --> 06:27.800
Say that again.

06:30.080 --> 06:32.280
I finally got

06:32.360 --> 06:34.160
an internship offer.

06:34.240 --> 06:36.600
It's hard to get an internship offer here.

06:36.680 --> 06:38.640
I finally landed one.
Of course I need to go.

06:38.720 --> 06:40.560
Besides, Dad and Mom have agreed to this.

06:40.640 --> 06:41.720
You get one more chance.

06:41.800 --> 06:42.760
Think before you speak.

06:42.840 --> 06:43.920
I already…

06:44.480 --> 06:46.320
I did think…

06:48.080 --> 06:49.760
I did think before I spoke.

06:49.840 --> 06:51.640
I'm not doing anything bad.

06:51.720 --> 06:52.920
Why are you acting like this?

06:53.600 --> 06:54.600
Fine.

06:54.680 --> 06:56.040
Do whatever you want.

06:56.120 --> 06:58.240
Listen, if you get scammed again,

06:58.320 --> 06:59.920
don't you come to me sobbing.

07:00.000 --> 07:01.760
I don't have time for your nonsense again.

07:01.840 --> 07:04.120
Why would I be scammed?

07:04.200 --> 07:06.960
Your rebellious phase is so long.

07:07.440 --> 07:10.320
You've been rebelling since 11th grade.

07:10.400 --> 07:12.160
Listen, you were dumb to begin with.

07:12.240 --> 07:13.880
Once you date, you're even more dumb.

07:16.280 --> 07:18.880
I'm dumb?

07:19.360 --> 07:20.560
I'm…

07:24.360 --> 07:25.400
I'm better than you.

07:25.480 --> 07:26.880
You have to announce to the world

07:26.960 --> 07:28.000
that you're dating.

07:28.080 --> 07:29.320
Do you want to pick a fight?

07:29.400 --> 07:31.040
You started it first.

07:31.120 --> 07:33.480
If you were sensible enough,
I wouldn't need to meddle.

07:33.560 --> 07:34.520
Think about it.

07:35.480 --> 07:37.160
Fine. You can do whatever you like.

07:37.240 --> 07:38.880
You can date all you want.

07:38.960 --> 07:40.280
Don't come to me again.

07:43.720 --> 07:45.080
Was that your brother?

07:46.160 --> 07:47.800
My immature brother.

07:47.880 --> 07:50.520
Your brother is really strict.

07:50.600 --> 07:51.520
You're an adult now.

07:52.440 --> 07:53.320
I mean,

07:53.400 --> 07:55.880
he is this mad
just because you're not going home.

07:55.960 --> 07:57.880
If he finds out
that you're dating an older guy,

07:58.640 --> 08:00.560
won't he blow up at you?

08:01.280 --> 08:02.400
I don't think he will.

08:02.480 --> 08:03.680
They're close friends.

08:03.760 --> 08:04.960
Are you sure?

08:09.320 --> 08:10.320
Good luck.

08:13.520 --> 08:16.200
He knows Duan Jiaxu well.

08:18.600 --> 08:19.680
Never mind.

08:19.760 --> 08:21.000
I'll be honest with him.

08:22.200 --> 08:24.200
I'm sure he will trust Duan Jiaxu.

08:25.280 --> 08:26.680
SANG ZHI

08:26.760 --> 08:27.680
Sang Yan.

08:27.760 --> 08:29.400
You don't have to worry about me.

08:29.480 --> 08:31.520
I just want to intern over the summer

08:32.080 --> 08:34.000
to gain experience
in the animation industry.

08:34.640 --> 08:36.280
I'll be home for Golden Week.

08:37.559 --> 08:39.559
I lied to you earlier.

08:39.640 --> 08:42.360
My boyfriend isn't
a postgraduate student here.

08:44.360 --> 08:45.840
You know him too.

08:45.920 --> 08:47.240
He's Jiaxu.

08:48.640 --> 08:50.120
Not some bad person.

08:50.200 --> 08:51.760
MESSAGE REJECTED BY RECIPIENT

08:54.520 --> 08:56.000
MESSAGE REJECTED BY RECIPIENT

09:11.040 --> 09:13.480
CHAPTER 19, LEAN IN CLOSE

09:13.560 --> 09:15.080
THE RHYTHM OF HAPPINESS

09:17.480 --> 09:18.560
You're our first intern

09:18.640 --> 09:19.760
who is a college freshman.

09:19.840 --> 09:21.560
Why are you interning so early?

09:21.640 --> 09:23.560
I just want to gain some experience.

09:24.440 --> 09:26.320
That's great. You're so proactive already.

09:27.760 --> 09:29.040
Is this your first internship?

09:33.440 --> 09:35.840
Our company mainly focuses
on animation design and management.

09:35.920 --> 09:37.720
Some of our clients are advertising firms

09:37.800 --> 09:38.920
or relevant media.

09:39.000 --> 09:41.160
Other clients are agencies and firms.

09:41.760 --> 09:43.120
This is the Planning Department.

09:43.200 --> 09:44.440
That is your seat, Sang Zhi.

09:44.520 --> 09:45.640
That is your seat, Wan Zhe.

09:47.880 --> 09:49.280
Where is Wang Yun?

09:49.360 --> 09:52.000
The client called me again last night
to complain.

09:52.080 --> 09:54.000
If you can't understand his requirements,

09:54.080 --> 09:55.320
call and ask until you do, okay?

09:55.400 --> 09:57.560
Xiaoyu, I've made an appointment
with Mr. Chen.

09:57.640 --> 09:59.320
We'll get his approval today. Don't worry.

10:00.440 --> 10:02.800
That is Shi Xiaoyu,
the head of the Planning Department.

10:04.840 --> 10:05.880
Nice to meet you, Xiaoyu.

10:10.240 --> 10:11.200
Who are you?

10:11.280 --> 10:12.520
What's wrong with you?

10:12.600 --> 10:13.880
And what's wrong with you?

10:13.960 --> 10:15.200
It's none of your business!

10:15.280 --> 10:16.520
Do you know why I did that?

10:16.600 --> 10:18.520
I don't care why.

10:19.480 --> 10:21.840
Xiaoyu, I'm Wan Zhe, a new intern.

10:23.240 --> 10:24.080
I'm…

10:25.720 --> 10:27.600
- I'm an intern.
- Our department

10:27.680 --> 10:29.240
is the design hub of the company.

10:29.800 --> 10:32.000
All projects start
at the Planning Department.

10:32.080 --> 10:33.040
After we get a project,

10:33.120 --> 10:35.560
we're the liaison between
the Design Department and our clients.

10:36.120 --> 10:38.160
Your job scope is to assist us

10:38.240 --> 10:39.320
in project development.

10:40.400 --> 10:41.800
Sang Zhi, this is your staff badge.

10:41.880 --> 10:42.720
Thank you.

10:43.240 --> 10:44.640
Here you go, Wan Zhe.

10:44.720 --> 10:46.280
- Thank you.
- You'll assist me, Xiaowan.

10:46.360 --> 10:48.120
Sang Zhi, you're with Xiaoyu.

10:49.240 --> 10:50.160
Come on.

10:51.640 --> 10:52.760
Where have you interned?

10:52.840 --> 10:54.320
I've interned at a few companies.

10:54.400 --> 10:55.600
All right, let's get started.

10:57.960 --> 10:59.000
This one…

10:59.080 --> 11:00.920
Put some colors and see.

11:01.000 --> 11:02.400
Make some adjustments.

11:13.160 --> 11:14.520
Hello, Xiaoyu.

11:14.600 --> 11:16.760
I'm the new intern, Sang Zhi.

11:16.840 --> 11:17.800
If you need anything--

11:17.880 --> 11:19.320
Make ten copies of these three files.

11:19.400 --> 11:21.240
Double-sided, side mount. Any questions?

11:22.320 --> 11:23.400
No.

11:24.680 --> 11:27.160
I want the copies by 10:00 a.m.
in the meeting room.

11:27.240 --> 11:28.520
And prepare tea for the clients.

11:28.600 --> 11:29.440
All right.

11:33.040 --> 11:34.200
Why are you still here?

11:58.360 --> 11:59.760
We still need to amend this.

12:00.920 --> 12:03.120
His head is too big.

12:03.200 --> 12:04.640
The proportions look off.

12:04.720 --> 12:05.600
I'll amend it.

12:10.760 --> 12:11.880
Are you having trouble?

12:14.520 --> 12:15.920
If you don't know something, just ask.

12:16.000 --> 12:17.720
We prioritize efficiency here.

12:19.600 --> 12:21.440
- Help her with it.
- Okay.

12:23.400 --> 12:24.680
Thank you. I'm sorry.

12:24.760 --> 12:25.760
It's okay.

12:40.400 --> 12:41.960
ZHIZHI'S FIRST DAY OF INTERNSHIP

12:42.040 --> 12:43.600
RED PACKET FROM DAD, EMPTY

12:43.680 --> 12:44.880
SILLY DOG

12:49.760 --> 12:50.760
RED PACKET FROM DAD, EMPTY

12:50.840 --> 12:52.000
SILLY DOG

12:55.480 --> 12:56.720
What's the matter?

12:56.800 --> 12:57.680
SANG ZHI

12:57.760 --> 12:58.640
TO SANG YAN

12:59.600 --> 13:02.360
RED PACKET FROM DAD

13:02.440 --> 13:03.320
TOO LATE, IT'S EMPTY

13:03.400 --> 13:05.040
DAD

13:05.120 --> 13:07.400
Brat, all you do is bully your sister.

13:07.480 --> 13:08.480
What else can you do?

13:10.200 --> 13:11.040
Exactly!

13:11.120 --> 13:14.600
ANGRY

13:14.680 --> 13:17.080
How was your first day of work, Zhizhi?

13:19.960 --> 13:22.320
HOLD TO TALK

13:26.480 --> 13:28.400
Today was the first day of my internship.

13:28.480 --> 13:30.440
I'm quite happy

13:30.520 --> 13:33.920
because my coworkers treat me well.

13:34.400 --> 13:35.240
Also,

13:35.320 --> 13:38.080
the work isn't as dull as I expected.

13:38.160 --> 13:39.320
It's quite interesting.

14:01.040 --> 14:03.080
I knew you would arrive early.

14:03.160 --> 14:04.080
I'm not late, am I?

14:05.240 --> 14:06.200
No.

14:06.280 --> 14:07.120
What did you bring?

14:08.480 --> 14:09.360
Let me see.

14:10.440 --> 14:11.400
What?

14:19.520 --> 14:20.600
This is for you.

14:24.680 --> 14:27.200
You must be tired
after your first day of work.

14:28.240 --> 14:29.360
Sunflowers?

14:29.440 --> 14:31.040
- Do you like them?
- Why sunflowers?

14:31.600 --> 14:32.720
Sunflowers.

14:33.760 --> 14:36.240
I hope that your days at work

14:37.000 --> 14:38.240
will be bright like them.

14:39.600 --> 14:40.920
I like it.

14:41.000 --> 14:41.840
Good.

14:42.640 --> 14:44.320
Let's go. You must be hungry.

14:44.400 --> 14:45.320
No.

14:47.880 --> 14:49.080
Are you going to eat this?

14:49.160 --> 14:50.000
Is it yummy?

14:51.360 --> 14:52.200
It's good.

14:55.240 --> 14:57.440
Did you enjoy your first day at work?

14:59.640 --> 15:00.480
Was it tiring?

15:00.960 --> 15:03.320
Did they give you

15:03.400 --> 15:04.560
a manageable workload?

15:06.080 --> 15:07.840
How are your coworkers?

15:09.760 --> 15:10.840
Why are you laughing?

15:12.200 --> 15:14.080
You're acting like…

15:16.240 --> 15:17.920
- Like what?
- A dad.

15:19.120 --> 15:21.160
Don't you think you're naggy?

15:21.240 --> 15:22.240
You're really long-winded.

15:22.320 --> 15:23.600
You have a lot of questions.

15:24.720 --> 15:26.120
Do you find me naggy now?

15:28.200 --> 15:29.360
Never mind.

15:29.440 --> 15:30.400
Here.

15:35.280 --> 15:37.240
You don't have to worry about me.

15:37.320 --> 15:38.760
I'm working now.

15:38.840 --> 15:40.160
I'm a mature adult.

15:40.240 --> 15:41.680
I'm no longer a child.

15:44.920 --> 15:46.120
A mature adult.

15:47.400 --> 15:48.360
Very well.

15:50.200 --> 15:51.080
Well,

15:52.800 --> 15:54.360
I have a gift for our little adult.

15:56.480 --> 15:57.560
It's so cute!

15:58.040 --> 15:59.200
Doesn't it look like you?

16:00.000 --> 16:01.200
Is this

16:02.280 --> 16:03.160
a pig?

16:04.560 --> 16:06.320
It's a rabbit! How is it a pig?

16:06.400 --> 16:07.680
Its ears are so big.

16:07.760 --> 16:09.160
It looks like a pig though.

16:11.360 --> 16:12.440
It looks like Sang Yan.

16:17.440 --> 16:18.920
I got this for you

16:19.000 --> 16:20.160
because I remembered

16:20.880 --> 16:22.800
when I first started my internship,

16:22.880 --> 16:24.240
I was lost and clueless.

16:24.320 --> 16:25.640
I was stressed out every day.

16:26.200 --> 16:27.360
I tended to doubt myself.

16:28.480 --> 16:31.160
So I hope that you won't experience this.

16:31.240 --> 16:33.800
I hope you can be happy
and everything will go well.

16:35.840 --> 16:37.040
And I know

16:37.640 --> 16:39.560
that you stayed for the internship

16:39.640 --> 16:42.640
so you can spend more time with me.

16:44.800 --> 16:46.240
If you're upset,

16:46.320 --> 16:47.640
you can vent to it.

16:48.200 --> 16:49.440
It's great for relieving stress.

16:53.080 --> 16:54.240
Screw you, Sang Yan.

16:58.440 --> 16:59.600
Did you have a fight with him?

17:01.440 --> 17:02.440
How did you know?

17:03.720 --> 17:06.440
I'm not blind yet.

17:10.359 --> 17:11.800
He blocked my number.

17:11.880 --> 17:12.720
Why?

17:14.240 --> 17:15.880
He doesn't want me to stay here.

17:15.960 --> 17:17.119
He wants me to go home.

17:18.839 --> 17:19.760
Moreover,

17:21.480 --> 17:23.720
have you told him about us?

17:25.079 --> 17:26.760
I haven't told him yet.

17:26.839 --> 17:29.240
I planned to go back with you this summer

17:29.320 --> 17:30.360
to tell him about it.

17:30.440 --> 17:32.000
It's better to tell him in person.

17:32.800 --> 17:33.840
But now,

17:34.320 --> 17:36.280
I'll have to wait until Golden Week

17:36.360 --> 17:37.560
to go back with you.

17:39.280 --> 17:41.120
We need to be sincere.

17:45.120 --> 17:46.240
Don't worry about it.

17:46.320 --> 17:47.720
Just leave it to me.

17:50.720 --> 17:52.080
He's so childish.

17:52.160 --> 17:54.000
He's really childish.

17:55.280 --> 17:57.320
I guess I'll need to buy a new one soon.

18:02.040 --> 18:03.920
JULY 2ND, MONDAY

18:04.000 --> 18:05.800
DON'T DOUBT YOURSELF

18:05.880 --> 18:09.960
HAPPILY FACE THE CHALLENGES

18:11.080 --> 18:13.200
On the cosmetic ad's creative direction,

18:13.280 --> 18:15.040
I want to hear everyone's ideas.

18:15.120 --> 18:16.240
But I have two requirements.

18:16.320 --> 18:17.960
It needs to be more immersive.

18:18.040 --> 18:19.000
Any other ideas?

18:20.520 --> 18:22.640
Perhaps we can use cold colors
like blue or green.

18:22.720 --> 18:23.560
Okay.

18:23.640 --> 18:25.840
Handle this. Leave this for next time.

18:45.040 --> 18:46.280
Take care of these.

19:02.120 --> 19:03.960
Xiaowan, are you done with the report?

19:05.480 --> 19:06.800
- Yes.
- Let me have a look.

19:09.840 --> 19:11.200
Okay. Good job.

19:11.280 --> 19:12.680
- I'll treat you to a meal.
- Okay.

19:16.520 --> 19:18.320
Sang Zhi, why don't you eat first?

19:18.400 --> 19:19.600
You can work on it later.

19:19.680 --> 19:20.880
I'll pass.

19:21.480 --> 19:22.840
Okay. Good luck.

19:53.080 --> 19:54.040
Hello?

19:54.960 --> 19:56.440
Are you going out to eat yet?

19:56.520 --> 19:58.960
Not yet. I'll go after I'm done working.

19:59.040 --> 19:59.880
Have you eaten?

20:00.840 --> 20:02.400
I have a meeting later.

20:02.480 --> 20:04.120
I'm afraid I won't have time to call you.

20:04.200 --> 20:06.760
You can let me know after you're done.

20:06.840 --> 20:07.800
Okay.

20:07.880 --> 20:09.120
Are you not done yet?

20:09.600 --> 20:11.400
If so, why are you on the phone?

20:12.160 --> 20:13.520
I'll call you later.

20:17.200 --> 20:18.600
I'm sorry.

20:21.000 --> 20:23.360
Don't do personal stuff during work hours.

20:23.440 --> 20:24.280
Okay.

20:32.560 --> 20:33.440
Jiaxu.

20:33.520 --> 20:34.760
Li Xun asks you over.

20:34.840 --> 20:36.080
Siyun is on a video call.

20:36.160 --> 20:37.640
- Come on.
- Okay. You can go first.

20:37.720 --> 20:38.600
Come on, let's go.

20:48.320 --> 20:50.160
Yawen, I'm clocking out now.

20:50.240 --> 20:51.960
My boyfriend is here to pick me up. Bye.

20:58.960 --> 21:00.320
Can you get off work early today?

21:01.840 --> 21:03.920
I think so.

21:04.000 --> 21:06.840
I plan to pick my boyfriend up from work
to give him a surprise.

21:07.440 --> 21:08.920
Okay, I'll leave first.

21:09.000 --> 21:10.120
- Bye. See you tomorrow.
- Bye.

21:15.760 --> 21:17.000
Xiaoyu.

21:17.720 --> 21:19.800
I've organized the invoices.
Where do I place them?

21:19.880 --> 21:21.280
Just put them on my desk.

21:22.720 --> 21:23.800
There's another box here.

21:23.880 --> 21:24.920
Finish it before you leave.

21:37.600 --> 21:38.520
Are you leaving?

21:39.280 --> 21:40.400
- Let's go.
- We're leaving.

21:40.480 --> 21:41.600
- Bye.
- Bye.

21:48.560 --> 21:49.760
Don't stay too late, Sang Zhi.

21:49.840 --> 21:50.880
- Bye.
- Bye, Pengxing.

21:55.640 --> 21:57.600
You're so hardworking, Sang Zhi.

21:57.680 --> 21:58.880
- Bye.
- Bye.

22:12.760 --> 22:15.680
Why is it giving an error again?

22:15.760 --> 22:17.000
Am I a Powerpuff Girl?

22:17.080 --> 22:18.600
I keep battling errors.

22:20.080 --> 22:22.520
I don't think
I'll survive until launch day.

22:31.640 --> 22:33.600
Jiaxu.

22:34.600 --> 22:35.520
Jiaxu.

22:37.600 --> 22:38.640
Don't look at me.

22:39.160 --> 22:41.160
I still have a lot on my plate.

22:41.720 --> 22:43.040
You two must be why

22:43.120 --> 22:44.920
Siyun is out of commission.

22:45.760 --> 22:46.760
That won't happen.

22:47.480 --> 22:48.760
Do you want a drink?

22:48.840 --> 22:50.120
You'll be recharged.

22:50.600 --> 22:51.600
Here, have a sip.

22:54.680 --> 22:56.240
Spill it. What's the problem?

22:56.320 --> 22:57.240
It's an error message.

22:57.880 --> 22:58.720
Error message?

23:01.000 --> 23:02.240
- Let me see.
- Dinner is here.

23:02.320 --> 23:03.280
You've all worked hard.

23:04.160 --> 23:06.320
- Thank you.
- But I have no idea.

23:06.400 --> 23:08.320
- Try it.
- There's a food delivery for you, Jiaxu.

23:09.200 --> 23:10.360
I didn't order anything.

23:10.960 --> 23:12.280
It's yours.

23:26.240 --> 23:27.120
What?

23:27.800 --> 23:30.000
Is it from your girlfriend?

23:30.080 --> 23:32.240
- What did she order?
- You're so lucky!

23:32.320 --> 23:33.320
Here, let me have a look.

23:33.400 --> 23:35.000
- Hurry up.
- Give me some.

23:35.720 --> 23:36.880
Do you still want my help?

23:36.960 --> 23:38.240
Eat your own food.

23:39.000 --> 23:41.040
- Come on.
- Let's eat.

23:41.120 --> 23:42.120
Let's eat our own food.

23:42.200 --> 23:43.400
Come on.

24:11.480 --> 24:12.400
Hello?

24:13.160 --> 24:14.280
Hello.

24:14.360 --> 24:15.880
Is the food delivery from you?

24:16.800 --> 24:18.960
Of course. Who else could it be?

24:19.840 --> 24:20.800
Have you eaten it yet?

24:21.480 --> 24:22.800
Not yet.

24:22.880 --> 24:23.960
If you ordered it for me,

24:24.040 --> 24:25.560
I'll eat it.

24:26.480 --> 24:28.400
Eat up then.

24:36.440 --> 24:37.760
You ordered so much.

24:40.080 --> 24:40.960
Is it good?

24:42.600 --> 24:43.480
It's delicious.

24:43.560 --> 24:46.440
After you finish it,
remember to take a photo

24:46.520 --> 24:48.080
so I can see how much you ate.

24:49.240 --> 24:50.080
Okay.

24:50.160 --> 24:51.360
Are you still here, Sang Zhi?

24:52.200 --> 24:53.440
Why are you back?

24:53.520 --> 24:54.440
I'm getting something.

24:54.520 --> 24:56.280
Remember to turn off the lights later.

24:56.360 --> 24:57.200
Sure.

24:58.040 --> 24:58.960
What are you doing?

24:59.800 --> 25:01.560
I'm working.

25:02.080 --> 25:04.720
I haven't finished some assigned tasks.

25:05.280 --> 25:06.400
Have you eaten?

25:06.480 --> 25:07.480
I've had my dinner.

25:07.560 --> 25:09.800
I'm so full today.

25:11.280 --> 25:13.760
I think I probably need

25:17.400 --> 25:18.440
about

25:20.480 --> 25:23.320
two more hours until I'm done.

25:24.320 --> 25:25.560
I'll go to you now.

25:25.640 --> 25:26.600
Wait for me.

25:27.840 --> 25:29.760
Aren't you busy? Why are you coming?

25:30.400 --> 25:31.960
No, I'm done already.

25:32.040 --> 25:33.080
I'll go to you now.

25:33.160 --> 25:34.520
Eat your dinner first.

25:34.600 --> 25:36.920
- Besides, I still have work to do.
- I'll see you in a bit.

25:38.760 --> 25:39.640
Bye.

26:18.600 --> 26:19.880
You can lean on my shoulder.

26:27.280 --> 26:28.120
How is it?

26:28.760 --> 26:29.760
You've worked all day.

26:29.840 --> 26:30.800
Are you tired?

26:44.320 --> 26:45.680
I have a question.

26:49.200 --> 26:50.120
Have you really

26:51.600 --> 26:53.280
never had a girlfriend?

26:58.400 --> 26:59.360
Have you?

27:00.760 --> 27:01.640
No.

27:02.960 --> 27:03.920
Wait.

27:04.000 --> 27:05.480
Why do you ask?

27:07.680 --> 27:08.600
Well,

27:10.000 --> 27:11.120
it suddenly came to mind.

27:13.920 --> 27:14.880
Hold on.

27:16.360 --> 27:19.240
Did someone speak ill of me?

27:22.400 --> 27:24.880
I have eyes around you.

27:24.960 --> 27:26.840
I know whatever you do.

27:28.520 --> 27:29.640
Eyes?

27:29.720 --> 27:30.840
I get it.

27:31.400 --> 27:32.560
Who doesn't have that?

27:34.040 --> 27:35.880
The guy that sits on your left

27:35.960 --> 27:38.800
is a short-haired fatty with glasses.

27:41.960 --> 27:42.960
Did I guess it right?

27:43.040 --> 27:43.960
Of course not.

27:44.040 --> 27:45.600
Silly.

27:49.720 --> 27:50.560
Dummy.

27:51.240 --> 27:52.440
I was just tricking you.

27:53.600 --> 27:54.600
Be careful.

27:54.680 --> 27:56.000
I'm watching

27:56.560 --> 27:58.120
your male coworkers.

28:17.360 --> 28:19.000
You should feel

28:19.080 --> 28:21.360
rather different now.

28:23.040 --> 28:24.640
In school,

28:25.200 --> 28:26.720
though there are a lot of schoolmates,

28:26.800 --> 28:29.120
the social circle is smaller and simpler.

28:29.800 --> 28:31.520
Now that you're in a company,

28:32.440 --> 28:34.920
every department has its own agenda.

28:35.400 --> 28:37.480
You also have superiors and bosses.

28:39.160 --> 28:40.560
No matter what they say,

28:40.640 --> 28:42.240
let it roll off your back.

28:42.320 --> 28:44.320
Your job is to observe and learn.

28:44.960 --> 28:46.280
Don't take anything to heart.

28:47.000 --> 28:48.760
You're still an intern anyway.

28:50.000 --> 28:51.000
Okay?

28:54.000 --> 28:55.280
You're so strange.

28:56.360 --> 28:59.440
I was so tired from work today.

29:00.320 --> 29:01.680
But after seeing you,

29:01.760 --> 29:03.840
I feel recharged.

29:05.200 --> 29:06.480
Are you fully charged now?

29:10.960 --> 29:11.920
Well,

29:12.560 --> 29:13.600
I also want to recharge.

29:21.000 --> 29:22.400
Are you fully charged now?

29:22.480 --> 29:23.480
Not yet.

29:24.480 --> 29:25.720
How about now?

29:27.480 --> 29:28.680
Let me charge a little longer.

29:50.920 --> 29:52.360
Your phone has been ringing.

29:58.960 --> 30:01.120
You should answer it, intern.

30:07.040 --> 30:08.080
Is it your boss?

30:11.320 --> 30:12.520
Hello, Xiaoyu.

30:21.240 --> 30:23.600
Okay, I'll do it tonight.

30:24.840 --> 30:25.760
Okay.

30:26.680 --> 30:27.640
I'll bring it tomorrow.

30:27.720 --> 30:29.760
Jiaxu, Li Xun is at the office.

30:29.840 --> 30:30.920
JIA YANG

30:37.200 --> 30:38.480
Let's go.

30:38.560 --> 30:39.640
I'll give you a ride.

30:41.080 --> 30:42.000
Okay.

30:43.560 --> 30:45.160
Intern.

30:46.240 --> 30:48.200
Do interns get this much work?

30:48.280 --> 30:50.320
Didn't you have work
when you were an intern?

30:51.040 --> 30:52.560
So internships…

30:55.040 --> 30:56.960
There's always a learning curve.

31:12.080 --> 31:13.080
SANG ZHI

31:13.160 --> 31:14.280
Are you going to sleep now?

31:17.040 --> 31:17.880
DUAN JIAXU

31:17.960 --> 31:19.480
Yes. What about you?

31:20.200 --> 31:21.640
Are you done with your work?

31:21.720 --> 31:22.720
Rest early.

31:24.440 --> 31:27.200
SANG ZHI

31:27.280 --> 31:29.560
I still have some work to do.

31:30.360 --> 31:31.480
You can sleep first.

31:31.960 --> 31:33.440
I'll sleep after I'm done.

31:34.000 --> 31:34.880
Good night.

32:09.880 --> 32:11.040
You're up, Jiaxu.

32:11.120 --> 32:12.040
Jiaxu.

32:13.000 --> 32:14.000
Where have you guys been?

32:16.000 --> 32:17.280
We went out to buy supper.

32:17.360 --> 32:18.800
We didn't want to wake you.

32:19.360 --> 32:20.480
Jiaxu, here is supper.

32:20.560 --> 32:21.920
- Come.
- Come on. Eat with us.

32:22.000 --> 32:23.000
- Join us.
- Come on.

32:23.080 --> 32:24.120
We can work after supper.

32:24.880 --> 32:25.800
- Let's go.
- Come on.

32:48.320 --> 32:49.480
ALARM

33:09.640 --> 33:10.880
Why are you here?

33:11.360 --> 33:12.640
I'll drive you to work.

33:13.400 --> 33:14.560
Why didn't you tell me?

33:15.160 --> 33:16.080
Hop in.

33:21.240 --> 33:22.320
Breakfast.

33:25.360 --> 33:26.360
Let's go.

33:41.280 --> 33:42.680
Did you sleep well yesterday?

33:49.720 --> 33:50.680
What's wrong?

33:57.400 --> 33:58.560
Your outfit is the same.

33:59.240 --> 34:00.720
You look tired.

34:00.800 --> 34:02.880
What did you do last night?

34:03.360 --> 34:04.920
Didn't we bid each other a good night?

34:06.280 --> 34:07.240
Look.

34:08.320 --> 34:10.480
If you have another girlfriend,

34:10.560 --> 34:11.480
you should let me know

34:11.560 --> 34:12.880
otherwise, you'll be tired.

34:12.960 --> 34:14.639
You would have to be with me
during the day

34:14.719 --> 34:16.600
and spend the night
with another girlfriend.

34:16.679 --> 34:18.600
No. Sang Zhi, I…

34:19.639 --> 34:22.000
I have many sets of this outfit.

34:23.080 --> 34:24.360
Besides, for a girlfriend,

34:25.320 --> 34:26.960
you are more than enough for me.

34:31.000 --> 34:32.880
Don't try to change the topic.

34:32.960 --> 34:34.159
Be honest with me.

34:35.639 --> 34:37.440
Did you work through the night?

34:39.120 --> 34:40.080
No.

34:53.120 --> 34:54.520
I did work overtime,

34:54.600 --> 34:55.920
but not through the night.

34:56.000 --> 34:57.400
I did sleep.

34:57.480 --> 34:59.720
I didn't want you to worry about me,

34:59.800 --> 35:02.000
so I didn't tell you about it.

35:05.560 --> 35:06.480
I know.

35:06.560 --> 35:08.880
I'll inform you in advance from now on.

35:08.960 --> 35:10.480
- Is that okay?
- That's not it.

35:11.440 --> 35:12.680
You could've told me.

35:12.760 --> 35:13.800
You didn't have to come.

35:13.880 --> 35:15.480
You could've slept in.

35:15.560 --> 35:16.600
No way.

35:17.120 --> 35:19.120
I must still drive you to work.

35:39.800 --> 35:41.120
Listen.

35:41.200 --> 35:43.880
You must nap before going to work, okay?

35:43.960 --> 35:45.080
Got it.

35:45.560 --> 35:46.680
Keep at it, intern.

35:47.880 --> 35:49.480
You remind me every day

35:49.560 --> 35:51.000
not to skip my meals.

35:51.080 --> 35:52.760
You should heed your word too.

35:53.640 --> 35:54.800
Otherwise, I'll get mad.

35:54.880 --> 35:55.880
Okay.

35:58.040 --> 35:59.120
Bye.

36:13.800 --> 36:15.040
See you.

36:15.120 --> 36:16.040
Bye.

36:53.840 --> 36:55.120
- Hold on.
- Okay.

36:58.040 --> 36:59.560
Hi, Xiaoyu. What is it?

37:00.240 --> 37:01.520
Nothing much.

37:01.600 --> 37:02.760
I have a question.

37:02.840 --> 37:04.160
Are you still in contact

37:04.240 --> 37:05.800
with Duan Jiaxu?

37:07.480 --> 37:08.960
Why do you ask about him?

37:09.520 --> 37:11.600
I just saw him outside my office building.

37:13.160 --> 37:15.040
He's outside your office building?

37:15.640 --> 37:17.680
Do you still remember that dinner?

37:18.200 --> 37:20.320
He was with a girl.

37:20.400 --> 37:22.000
That girl threw water on you.

37:22.960 --> 37:25.240
She is now interning at my company.

37:26.120 --> 37:27.120
I saw

37:27.800 --> 37:29.200
that they're quite close.

37:30.920 --> 37:32.280
Excuse me for a minute.

37:38.720 --> 37:39.800
Are they in a relationship?

37:41.040 --> 37:42.080
Are you okay?

37:44.160 --> 37:45.040
I'm okay.

37:46.480 --> 37:48.120
Should I come and meet you now?

37:51.640 --> 37:53.800
I'm really fine. Go to work, Xiaoyu.

37:53.880 --> 37:55.720
All right. I'll talk to you later.

37:55.800 --> 37:56.760
Bye.

38:06.840 --> 38:09.160
Has Xiaoyu given you her feedback
on the slides?

38:12.120 --> 38:14.560
I submitted it to her last night,

38:14.640 --> 38:16.360
but she hasn't replied yet.

38:17.360 --> 38:19.440
She's taking a long time to reply.

38:21.160 --> 38:22.160
Well, who knows?

38:22.640 --> 38:24.840
Maybe she has no issues with it
and approves it.

38:28.680 --> 38:29.880
Sang Zhi.

38:30.520 --> 38:31.480
Please come over.

38:39.880 --> 38:41.600
Is this your first proposal?

38:43.840 --> 38:45.400
The client will be seeing this.

38:45.480 --> 38:46.640
The most basic requirement

38:46.720 --> 38:48.040
is a simple yet persuasive layout

38:48.120 --> 38:50.400
with clear and concise data
for quick understanding.

38:50.480 --> 38:52.000
Look at the title's font.

38:52.080 --> 38:54.400
It's huge while the content is tiny.

38:55.360 --> 38:56.600
Noted.

38:56.680 --> 38:58.560
You said that the font size must follow--

38:58.640 --> 39:00.720
I told you not to act on your own.

39:00.800 --> 39:02.400
Did I say to be an inflexible fool?

39:03.280 --> 39:04.360
Xiaoyu.

39:05.880 --> 39:07.880
Help me take a look at Jiajia's draft.

39:07.960 --> 39:08.920
It's really urgent.

39:11.640 --> 39:12.640
Amend it at once.

39:12.720 --> 39:14.560
Revise it following the original template.

39:15.040 --> 39:17.880
Remember, keep it simple and organized.

39:17.960 --> 39:18.920
Do you understand?

39:25.960 --> 39:27.080
What's wrong with you?

39:27.640 --> 39:28.720
She's just an intern.

39:28.800 --> 39:29.960
Why are you so harsh to her?

39:58.960 --> 39:59.960
Xiaoyu.

40:00.960 --> 40:02.960
You don't seem to like Sang Zhi.

40:05.400 --> 40:08.000
Look, we finally have two interns.

40:08.640 --> 40:10.800
Sang Zhi seems quite smart and obedient.

40:10.880 --> 40:13.080
Don't scare her away in less than a month.

40:13.160 --> 40:14.200
Obedient?

40:14.280 --> 40:17.080
You don't know
what she is like in private.

40:17.560 --> 40:19.000
Judging by your words,

40:19.080 --> 40:21.120
you seem to have a big problem with her.

40:23.120 --> 40:25.320
She doesn't know anything,
but acts like she does.

40:26.000 --> 40:27.360
I just can't stand her.

41:02.880 --> 41:04.040
Hello, Xiaoying.

41:06.120 --> 41:07.240
Hello, Xiaoyu.

41:07.880 --> 41:09.560
Let's have dinner together later.

41:10.120 --> 41:11.920
Tonight? I can't make it tonight.

41:12.000 --> 41:13.480
My company has a team-building event.

41:15.640 --> 41:16.480
Where?

41:17.880 --> 41:19.760
It's at the KTV that we frequent.

41:22.480 --> 41:23.640
I'll talk to you later.

41:23.720 --> 41:25.560
I need to go. Let's have dinner next time.

41:26.880 --> 41:28.480
Okay. Go on.

41:34.760 --> 41:36.720
- Fifteen!
- Ten!

41:37.360 --> 41:39.960
- Ten!
- Five!

41:40.040 --> 41:41.560
- Fifteen!
- Twenty!

41:42.200 --> 41:43.680
Come on! Drink!

41:44.520 --> 41:45.720
How much did you drink?

41:45.800 --> 41:50.200
DUAN JIAXU

41:50.280 --> 41:52.080
Not much. Just a little.

41:52.160 --> 41:53.920
SANG ZHI

41:54.000 --> 41:55.000
I'm so bored.

41:55.080 --> 41:56.040
I want to leave.

41:59.680 --> 42:00.800
Find an excuse.

42:00.880 --> 42:01.880
I'll pick you up.

42:02.640 --> 42:03.560
Okay.

42:06.240 --> 42:10.160
- I wait for you
- I wait for you

42:10.240 --> 42:14.160
- To pass me by unaware
- To pass me by unaware

42:16.160 --> 42:20.480
- Only then can I have a good dream
- Only then can I have a good dream

42:22.880 --> 42:25.480
- To compromise
- To compromise

42:25.560 --> 42:26.840
It's almost my dorm's curfew.

42:26.920 --> 42:28.160
Okay.

42:29.480 --> 42:31.360
- I'll get going first.
- Next song.

42:31.440 --> 42:32.880
- Goodbye.
- Next song.

42:32.960 --> 42:34.120
- Pick a song.
- Pass me the mic.

42:34.200 --> 42:35.920
Pass the mic, Mingming. This is mine.

43:03.440 --> 43:04.880
- Nothing good is nearby.
- Let's eat.

43:04.960 --> 43:06.680
- Everything is closed now.
- What did you get?

43:07.240 --> 43:08.720
Supper from one of the restaurants.

43:09.280 --> 43:10.280
Come and see.

43:12.560 --> 43:13.880
- Eat up.
- Dig in.

43:13.960 --> 43:15.400
- Here you go.
- Thanks.

43:19.400 --> 43:21.240
Just hang in there a little longer.

43:22.080 --> 43:23.400
It's always hard in the beginning.

43:23.480 --> 43:24.800
Back in the day, Li Xun and I

43:24.880 --> 43:26.600
always coded until sunrise.

43:27.240 --> 43:28.240
Eat up.

43:30.680 --> 43:32.600
I really miss my bed.

43:34.640 --> 43:35.600
I wonder

43:35.680 --> 43:37.080
if my fish are still alive.

43:37.160 --> 43:39.120
After this,

43:39.200 --> 43:40.280
I'll go to the beach,

43:40.360 --> 43:42.160
stay in the largest ocean-view suite,

43:42.240 --> 43:43.960
and enjoy the sunset.

43:44.040 --> 43:44.920
Sure.

43:45.000 --> 43:46.800
Send me the receipt for reimbursement.

43:46.880 --> 43:48.160
Really? Thank you, Jiaxu.

43:48.240 --> 43:49.640
Jiaxu.

43:49.720 --> 43:51.840
What are your plans after this?

43:53.240 --> 43:54.360
I'll move to a new place.

43:56.400 --> 43:57.320
After that,

43:59.160 --> 44:00.640
I'll spend time with my girlfriend.

44:04.520 --> 44:06.160
I want to have a girlfriend too.

44:07.160 --> 44:08.200
Well,

44:08.280 --> 44:10.160
you should wait until your program works.

44:10.240 --> 44:11.760
You're right.

44:11.840 --> 44:14.000
Let's eat quickly and get back to coding.

44:14.080 --> 44:16.120
When I get no more errors, love will come.

44:16.200 --> 44:17.400
Eat up.

44:17.480 --> 44:18.880
You don't have to be that serious.

44:18.960 --> 44:19.800
Eat up.

44:22.080 --> 44:23.560
Hurry up. Eat up.
